      "content": "yeah, we get that. but the consensus from the dev team is that the \"standardization\" approach is the only way to keep the brand safe and professional. we're moving ahead with a patch that maps those dialects more closely to standard English structures to eliminate the variance. basically, we're stripping out those idiosyncratic patterns to ensure consistency. we'll start the deployment tonight.",
